      \"step 4\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"claim\": \"P lies on line BC.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"From step 5, RP is the radical axis of O1 and O2, and from step 6 this radical axis is BC. Since P lies on RP, it follows that P lies on BC.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 5\",\n        \"step 6\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"P, B, and C are collinear.\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization."
